articles.title: 'Deal of the century': how UBS's rescue of Credit Suisse proved a boon - Financial Times
articles.description: Record $29bn quarterly profit linked to the takeover triggers fierce political debate in Switzerland
articles.content:
UBSs top managers were sceptical when they were forced to rescue their scandal-ridden rival Credit Suisse. Five months on, the deal has made the bank Europes second-most valuable lender.
